{"word":"Pilate, Pontius","slug":"pilate,-pontius","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pilate, Pontius</b> Roman governor of Judaea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=2'>Mat 27:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=1'>Luk 3:1</a><br/> Causes slaughter of certain Galileans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=1'>Luk 13:1</a><br/> Tries Jesus and orders His crucifixion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27'>Mat 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15'>Mar 15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23'>Luk 23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=40'>Joh 18:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19'>Joh 19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=13'>Act 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=27'>Act 4:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=28'>Act 13:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=6&verse=13'>1Ti 6:13</a><br/> Allows Joseph of Arimathaea to take Jesus' body<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=58'>Mat 27:58</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=45'>Mar 15:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=52'>Luk 23:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=38'>Joh 19:38</a>"}]}